Molajo will automatically load CSS and JS files according to these rules:

1. Application-specific CSS and JS in => media/site/[application]/css[js]/XYZ.css[js]
2. Component specific CSS and JS in => media/site/[application]/[com_component]/css[js]/XYZ.css[js]
3. Asset ID (for the page) specific CSS and JS in => media/site/[application]/[asset_id]/css[js]/XYZ.css[js]

Note:

a. Layouts have CSS and JS folders for automatically loading these files.
b. Name Right-to-left css files with rtl_ for Molajo to automatic load
